please fix the CI failure
Please check the bellow functions and update the params and function documentation docstring

why is 0xc0 value hardcoded here?

why not get the count of sdr_list itself?

1.As per the IPMI spec,
Table 43-11, OEM Record - SDR Type C0h
SDR type for OEM Record needs to be C0
 
2.The Objective for this function is to get count of SDR OEM Record. If there is no C0 in the list it will return 0
Have a question about 0xc0 hard code

As per Spec,0xc0 is the SDR OEM record. Sensor elist will not show SDR OEM record, SDR info will show the SDR OEM record. While comparing sensor elist and sdr info there will be a mismatch in the count. Hence from SDR elist returning OEM record count and subtracting that count in SDR info so that sdr info will have record count excluding SDR OEM record.
I'm a bit confused by this. Why are we only returning the count of 0xc0 record types? Is that the only type we want to count?  If so then this function needs a better name.
